{
  "texts": [
    "The RTE dataset has been included in GLUE and SuperGLUE, serving as an evaluation benchmark for English NLU tasks.",
    "• SNLI (Bowman et al, 2015).",
    "Human annotators have labeled the premises and hypotheses in the SNLI dataset by relying on image captions, resulting in a dataset of 570K text pairs.",
    "This dataset currently holds the record as the largest in scale for RTE.",
    "• WANLI (Liu et al, 2022)."
  ]
}